    <h2>    Welcome to our sports management application designed to cater to the needs of both administrators and players. Our platform aims to streamline the process of organizing and participating in sports sessions (matches) with user-friendly features tailored to different personas. Here's an overview of what our application offers:</h2>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Admins Can Create Sports:</strong> Administrators have the ability to create and manage various sports activities within the system. They can easily add new sports and manage existing ones.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Players Can Sign Up and Sign In:</strong> Players are provided with a seamless registration and authentication process. New users can sign up by providing basic information such as name, email address, and password. Existing users can conveniently sign in with their credentials.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Players Can Create a Sport Session:</strong> Players have the autonomy to create new sport sessions (matches) according to their preferences. They can choose from available sports, select players for each team, specify the number of additional players needed, and set the date, time, and venue for the session.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Players Can View and Join Existing Sport Sessions:</strong> Players can browse through a list of existing sport sessions created by other players and join sessions that match their interests. Once joined, their participation is marked, and their name is visible to others.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Admins Can Create a Sport Session:</strong> Administrators possess the same capabilities as regular players, allowing them to create and join sport sessions as needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p><strong>Players Can Cancel Their Created Sessions:</strong> Players who have initiated a sport session can cancel it if necessary, providing a reason for cancellation. This information is displayed to other players who had previously joined the session.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="marquee">
        <span>Welcome to the Sports Scheduler Application, where you can discover the perfect time to indulge in your favorite sport. Explore and plan your sporting activities with ease!</span>
